I have a question about the crawl.log (I'm using 1.2.0 Heritrix).

The user manual (section 8.2.1) describes 10 fields, whereas my
logs/crawl.log file seems to have 11 fields in each line.

Is the 10th field in the crawl.log some sort of fingerprint?

If it is, why/how do people use this?  If not, what is it?

Cheers, D. Bergmark
